                <p>
                    You can also download a copy of the paper.
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="@Url.Content("~/Documents/Kalokerinos_DontGrinWhenYouWin.pdf")" target="blank" onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Downloads', 'Paper_DontGrin', 'SPSP2014Poster']);">Don't grin when you win: The social costs of positive emotion expression in performance situations</a>
